{"tid":1434124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"爭取中間派、和理非支持嘅方法","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T16:30:36.000Z","uid":1965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6c8ae853f6dadf8f13b348f02df67ee64427ba","tid":1434124,"uid":1965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"就係繼續贏，佢地只係勝利球迷。<br />\n<br />\n文宣、連燶牆、放映會，已經有接觸到呢d人，兩個月都唔變就唔會變嫁喇。<br />\n<br />\n而加要做嘅係，繼續將增加政府管治成本，繼續破壞黑警嘅精神、士氣。<br />\n<br />\n你只要繼續贏落去，呢d人就會靠邊，勝利球迷就係咁。<br />\n<br />\n不要大台、不篤灰、不割席、不受傷、不被捕<br />\n<br />\n不分化係講緊不分化想贏嘅人，但一定要分化想散水嘅人！"},{"pid":"7bae66f5e24bad068f693a9076a27cdfb8c03072","tid":1434124,"uid":119485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5XqWt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5XqWt.png&h=2edd738f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dw1Dapa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDw1Dapa.jpg&h=f1f6aa56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQGGSEb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQGGSEb.jpg&h=f8cc4264&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKDJ5X5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKDJ5X5.jpg&h=efb6ebbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOSKQpb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOSKQpb.jpg&h=e6dcca84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cm36bK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcm36bK9.jpg&h=5ce2c060&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}